  <infoaction message='Saving

The Medregg sector is typically full of enemies; you&apos;re going to want to save your game before taking them on.   You can press &apos;escape&apos; while flying to go back to the main menu.  From there, press &apos;save game&apos; and your game will be saved.   When you start up Kuiper later, you can press &apos;load game&apos; to pick up where you left off.  To go right back to playing, press &apos;Resume game&apos;.  Your game will also automatically be saved when you take off from a planet.

You may also want weapons to deal with the alien menace.  Land on Earth to learn about them. ' tag='msg_instruct_saving' show_once_only='true' labels='' shown='false'/>
