  <infoaction message='Combat

When you press &apos;ok&apos; to this, you&apos;re likely to see a sector in turmoil.  Medreggi ships will be attacking Terrans, who are counting on you to help them.

You can target enemies a number of ways.  By clicking on them with the mouse, by cycling through all available targets with the &apos;tab&apos; key, or by pressing &apos;r&apos; to select the nearest hostile target.  While you have a target selected, your weapons will not affect any other targets, and if you don&apos;t have any targets ,your weapons will affect the first thing they hit, so be careful!

Ships targeting you will appear red on your radar.  Your shields will protect you from their fire and, when those are depleted, your armor.  If your armor is reduced to 0, the game is over.

This is the last portion of the tutorial.  Good luck! ' tag='msg_explain_combat' show_once_only='true' labels='' shown='false'/>
